text: St. Patrick's Day Slam (2023) was a professional wrestling show made by All Elite Wrestling (AEW). It took place on March 15, 2023 at the Canada Life Centre in Winnipeg, Manitoba, Canada. The event aired as a special episode of Rampage on March 17, 2023. It was the third St. Patrick's Day Slam event held by AEW. The main event of the show saw Daniel Garcia defeat Brody King. Garcia ended up distracting the referee and Jericho hit King with a baseball bat.
